author: Petula Martyn
title: DPD Ireland reports increase in online deliveries
description: Parcel delivery company DPD Ireland has seen a dramatic increase in online deliveries since government restrictions advising people to stay at home, were introduced.
content:
Parcel delivery company DPD Ireland has seen a dramatic increase in online deliveries since government restrictions advising people to stay at home, were introduced.
